headline: Celsius (CELH) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of energy drink company Celsius (NASDAQ:CELH) jumped 3.6% in the afternoon session after the company provided a positive business update ahead of a conference, highlighting strong market share growth and progress on integrating its Alani Nu brand with its PepsiCo distribution partner.
